Uthe lezi zigameko zihleliwe futhi zihambisana nobugebengu. Uqhube wathi abomthetho bafuna ukubamba abasusi bodweshu okuthiwa seludlule nabantu abevile ku-10. Bangaphezulu kuka-400 abantu asebeboshiwe esikhathini esiyisonto. UNkk Mapisa-Nqakula ulugxekile udlame wathi abantu abalufuqayo bayizigebengu. Amaphoyisa ayaqhubeka nokuqapha isimo ezindaweni ezike zagubuzelwa wudlame eGoli. NgeSonto ebusuku kuvele ukuthi kukhona isakhiwo esishisiwe, kwezinye izitolo kuthathwe impahla. Amaphoyisa anxuse ukuba abantu behlise umoya. Abanye abakhulume neSABC baveze ukuthi yize bengabakuleli kodwa abaphephile futhi bayaphazamiseka ezifundweni zabo nasemisebenzini ngenxa yalesi simo esiqhubekayo.  